features: ⭐Say Goodbye to Clutter: No enough space for your great storage needs? No way to face the awkward situation of small spaces at bathroom? Our bathroom cabinet provides a practical solution for you! This bathroom cabinet features an upper and a lower cabinet to provide ample space. All your bathroom essentials, from towels to toilet paper rolls to toiletries, will be organized within hands’ reach, offering you a tidy and enjoyable bathroom.

⭐Adjustable Shelves: Our bathroom floor cabinet features one adjustable interior shelf that you can adjust appropriately according to your personal preferences, giving you the flexibility to organize your own space without wasting extra space.

⭐All-Rounder Piece：Not only for the bathroom or laundry room, it can be placed in the kitchen to store the pots and pans. It can also go in the living room for books and picture frames, or in the entryway to hold out-the-door essentials…all up to you!

⭐Safety First: Painted MDF can withstand the humidity and prevent moisture, specially designed for humid occasions, perfect storage for bathroom and kitchen. Our panels are not only scratch, but they are CARB certified, formaldehyde free, greener, and more secure to use.

⭐Easy to Assemble: This freestanding cabinet can be installed simply and effortlessly. The detailed instructions, clearly labeled parts and necessary tools facilitate your assembly. Everything is done in minutes. Trust me, this cabinet will exceed your expectations.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The Perfect Solution for Keeping Your Home Organized and Clutter-free This bathroom floor cabinet featuring graceful minimalist finish design, not only give you plenty of space to store items, but also looks good in the home! This storage cabinet is capacious to quickly store your often-used items, bathroom toiletries, blankets, dolls or pet supplies etc, giving you a clean and organized house. Choose IWELL storage cabinet to be your assistant to tidy your rooms and drive your troubles of clutters away.

Customizable Storage There is both fixed and adjustable shelf in the storage cabinet, you can freely adjust the height to meet your various storage needs, or remove the shelf to store high bottle storage, allowing you to organize both tall and short items and keep them away from dust.

Living Room Cabinet In the living room, it conveniently accommodates collections and magazines while taking no additional floor space. Kitchen Pantry Cabinet In the kitchen, it gives you more room to store all of your wine bottles, seasoning cans, cutlery, food, pots in order within reach. Bookcase In the home office, it provides storage functions for your books and documents and etc. Bathroom Cabinet In the bathroom, it is perfect for extra storage, sort laundry detergents, cleaning towels and a sea of toiletries into an organized collection.

Detail Display Strong Magnetic Door User-friendly magnetic door holders make it easy to open and close, helping you to hide items and secrets behind doors. Round Metal Knob Metal craftsmanship handle can make sure durable even though touched with wet hand. Flexible Hinge Soft-close Hinge can help open the cabinet door with ease and pleasure. Adjustable Shelf The design of the shelf is adjustable, you can adjust it at any time according to the size of the placed items.

reviews.reviewText: Arrived with some cosmetic damage.It's relatively easy to assemble. The doors don't really align well.The pegs for the movable shelf fall out very easily.This seems like it could tip over and break at any moment. It's also not as big as they try to make it look in the pictures.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Easy assembly, but not high quality.
reviews.reviewText: Assembly was super easy dispite the fact that two of the pieces/hardware were labeled incorrectly... the pictures in the instructions were sufficient [I was a huge Ikea customer years ago, so going without words is no biggie to me]. The plywood was too soft on one piece, so the top doors ended up being slightly off/not squared... still worked, but my OCD just sees the variance. The cabinet holds a lot and has a clean look, so I'm keeping it for now, but will replace when I find a better quality product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I like it but it's a Lil shorter then I thought it would be but that's because my measurements was off so that was my fault on that part. It was easy to put together but I feel that for how the wood is and the size the price is just high. I bought a bigger/longer one a few years ago for the same price but the wood is not top quality for that type of price. I had to get new one cause the wood at the bottom broke off but for this product the price is high for not good wood quality that it is.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Read the Measurements
reviews.reviewText: Bought this cabinet to store our girls' toys in. Assembly was pretty straight-forward. While taking it out of the box, it was looking pretty small. After assembling it, I was extremely disappointed at how LITTLE this thing is. The pictures give the impression that the cabinet will be much larger with much more storage than it actually has. Not only is the thing crazy little, but it also tips over forward much too easily. Hard pass on this & returning it as soon as I disassemble it.
